        public int convertToMotorValue(double throttle)
        This method takes in a double which it compares to values of the objects array. The value in the array which has the smallest difference to the double is returned.
        Parameters:
        throttle - is a value which we compare to the values of the array to find the closest approximation
        Returns:
        the value in the array which is closest to the value of throttle
